item.description:
Venez bavarder avec nous!

Cafe on the Corner is on the west side of Central Avenue/Route 108, just south of the railroad tracks. It's on your right if you are driving south from Spaulding Exit 9; if you are driving north from a prior exit, you will have to turn left on or make a U-turn at the traffic light at Third Street.

Park in front of the Cafe on Central Avenue, around the corner on Third Street, or in a free municipal lot off of Third Street (next to the bank, across from the Strand cinema). Come on in and look for the Meetup sign on the table . . . or just listen for us! We try to claim a spot in the back of the main room, where the couches are.
